# discobot-redirect ‚Äî tiny https‚Üíobsidian:// deep-link bridge (stdlib only, no
# deps, no secrets). Exposed on the tailnet via `tailscale serve ‚Ä¶ /o`.
# Build context = ops/ :  docker build -f docker/redirect/Dockerfile -t discobot-redirect .
